This is a mind map exported from iMindQ.
The mind map is interactive, and you can:

  • - View the branches in depth
  • - Position the branches where you want
  • - Insert, delete and reparent topics
  • - Zoom in and zoom out
  • - Play the creation of the map
  • - Share your mind map on your blog, website, and in social media.
